ing: 4 cups baby spinach, rinsed and dried
2 small, cooked chicken breast, cut into small pieces
des: "An unusual combination I came up with one night while preparing my lunch for the next day. Was scared to try it, but it turned out to be good! You could replace any ingredient to make it your own."
ins: Toss together spinach, cucumber, broccoli, feta, onion, chicken, and bacon in a large bowl. Pour dressing over salad, and gently toss again.
